{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% block title %}I Had a Setback{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-indigo-950 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-lg w-full">

        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <a href="{{ path('app_dashboard') }}" class="text-white/50 hover:text-white/80 text-sm">← Back</a>
            <div class="text-6xl mt-6 mb-4">💙</div>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-white">It's okay.</h1>
            <p class="text-white/70 mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                A setback is not a failure.<br>
                It's information. It's human. It's part of recovery.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-3xl p-8 text-white mb-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <p>🔬 <strong>The science:</strong> Relapse rates for addiction are 40–60% — similar to diabetes and hypertension. It doesn't mean treatment failed. It means addiction is a chronic condition that requires ongoing care.</p>
            <p>🧠 <strong>What you keep:</strong> Every day you were clean built new neural pathways. Those don't disappear. Your brain is different now, and stronger, even after a slip.</p>
            <p>⚡ <strong>Your XP and achievements stay.</strong> Every insight you gained stays. Only the streak counter resets — and you know how to build that streak. You've done it.</p>
            <p>💪 <strong>Most importantly:</strong> You came here instead of pretending it didn't happen. That self-awareness is exactly what recovery looks like.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl">
            <h2 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-xl mb-6">Reset Your Streak</h2>

            <form method="POST" action="{{ path('app_relapse_confirm') }}" class="space-y-5">
                <input type="hidden" name="_token" value="{{ csrf_token('confirm_relapse') }}">

                {% if user.addictionType == 'both' %}
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">Which track are you resetting?</label>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
                        {% for val, label in {'alcohol': '🍷 Alcohol', 'cigarettes': '🚬 Cigarettes', 'both': '💪 Both'} %}
                        <label class="cursor-pointer" x-data>
                            <input type="radio" name="addiction_type" value="{{ val }}" class="sr-only"
                                   required
                                   x-on:change="$dispatch('track-change', '{{ val }}')">
                            <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-2.5 text-center text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 transition cursor-pointer hover:border-brand-400"
                                 x-on:track-change.window="$el.classList.toggle('border-brand-500', $event.detail === '{{ val }}'); $el.classList.toggle('bg-brand-50', $event.detail === '{{ val }}')">
                                {{ label }}
                            </div>
                        </label>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </div>
                {% else %}
                <input type="hidden" name="addiction_type" value="{{ user.addictionType }}">
                {% endif %}

                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1.5">
                        What happened? <span class="font-normal text-gray-400">(optional, for yourself)</span>
                    </label>
                    <textarea name="notes" rows="3"
                              class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-400 resize-none text-sm"
                              placeholder="What triggered it? What were you feeling? No judgment here — this is for your insight."></textarea>
                </div>

                <button type="submit"
                        class="w-full py-3.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-600 to-teal-600 text-white rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:opacity-90 transition">
                    Reset & Start Again Today
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center text-white/40 text-sm mt-6">
            "Healing is not linear. Getting back up is the victory."
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
